    LoggingEvents

    public class LoggingEvents.VoiceIme
extends java.lang.Object
    Logging event constants for VoiceIME. Below are the extra values for LoggingEvents.EXTRA_EVENT, clustered with keys to additional extras for some events that need to be included as additional fields in the event.
